12::[Boosts]::
2Boosts are special abilities that are attached to a weapon that you may purchase in the shop. Unlike regular techniques which are used to attack monsters (or in some cases to heal yourself or others), boosts may only be used on yourself and will increase your battle stats for the duration of the battle.
12::[How do I use a boost?]::
2IN BATTLE you may use the command /me goes <boost name>